ZH: 椅子是用来坐的。
EN: Chairs are used for sitting.
ZH: 这把椅子很舒适。
EN: This chair is very comfortable.
ZH: 请坐在椅子上。
EN: Please sit on the chair.
ZH: 她正在给椅子上的布料擦拭。
EN: She is wiping down the fabric on the chair.
ZH: 我们需要更多的椅子来容纳客人。
EN: We need more chairs to accommodate the guests.
ZH: 桌子旁边放了很多椅子。
EN: There are many chairs next to the table.
ZH: 他会在这把椅子上读书。
EN: He will read on this chair.
ZH: 这个椅子看起来很漂亮。
EN: This chair looks very pretty.
ZH: 椅子的背板很结实。
EN: The back of the chair is very sturdy.
ZH: 这张椅子上坐着一个小男孩。
EN: A little boy is sitting on this chair.
ZH: 在图书馆里有很多椅子供人们休息。
EN: There are many chairs in the library for people to rest.
ZH: 很多椅子都是木制的。
EN: Many chairs are made of wood.
ZH: 他们在修理坏了的椅子。
EN: They are fixing the broken chairs.
ZH: 这个房间里只有一把椅子。
EN: There is only one chair in this room.
ZH: 可以把这把椅子放在阳台上。
EN: You can put this chair on the balcony.
ZH: 这个椅子已经破了，需要修理。
EN: This chair is broken and needs repair.
ZH: 这次会议需要预备更多的椅子。
EN: We need to prepare more chairs for this meeting.
ZH: 现在大家都坐好了，就可以开始了。
EN: Now that everyone is seated, we can begin.
